title: Silver V+ - Looking to climb - DUO Partner
body:
**What's up?**

Looking for a serious partner who wants to team up, and use our roles and expertise thus far to grind up in ranks. Have had a long break from League and am returning with the roles: **_Jungle & Support._** I'm very team orientated and can understand people make mistakes, especially in these lower ranks. But if you're not learning and consistently making them, I'm sorry but you won't be a good fit for this partnership. _I'm looking for serious players only._ 

**Main Champs:** 
{{champion:203}} {{champion:16}} 

**Preferred Rank:** Silver V to Gold V
**Comms: **Discord
**Roles:** MID or TOP or ADC
**Champs:** _ANY_ - If you have an idea on a comp, let me know.
**First Goal:** Gold I 
**Second Goal: **Diamond III

Discord: **Zch#5429**
_*Please include " DUO " as a Reference when messaging me._
